item.title: read open source
item.description: Awesome project lists using Gin web framework: gorush: A push notification server written in Go. fnproject: The container native, cloud agnostic serverless platform. photoprism: Personal photo management powered by Go and Google TensorFlow. krakend: Ultra performant API Gateway with middlewares. picfit: An image resizing server written in Go. gotify: A simple server for sending and receiving messages in real-time per web socket. cds: Enterprise-Grade Continuous Delivery & DevOps Automation Open
